{"tid":1383253,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企兩老對示威者提出咗個問題 有冇人幫我答","createTime":"2019-07-29T16:00:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T10:27:09.000Z","uid":258387,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"53f46b5e2a43e57338ff31e250857dacaef48cc2","tid":1383253,"uid":258387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:00:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15c79cff2809615a92c2406a76e606590f8e3dcc","tid":1383253,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:03:20.000Z","msg":"圍你老母 6月講到口臭<br />\n<br />\n見依家個局開始靜 又想叫人衝?"},{"pid":"8f6102d10fb505886f725a900d37c6b40665dd3e","tid":1383253,"uid":89974,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"quote":{"pid":"53f46b5e2a43e57338ff31e250857dacaef48cc2","tid":1383253,"uid":258387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:00:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:03:29.000Z","msg":"因為而家已經係黑警同中共做終極大boss<br />\n林鄭係呢件事影響力已經壽終正寢<br />\n<br />\n你諗下連張建宗都會俾狗屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2c1f91c471a7ed22c36f7cc50e14688feaf3369","tid":1383253,"uid":33721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:04:40.000Z","msg":"柒婆算得乜 中共先係大佬"},{"pid":"4d1989bc270028ffbc18cc6625101432c90a9bd9","tid":1383253,"uid":270566,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:06:35.000Z","msg":"冇錯，港督府一定要去！<br />\n如果行普通嘅路線，一定比佢哋講咗入去後門。<br />\n應該幾線分開去，由上邊堅道，左邊堅尼地道，下邊花園道，蘭桂坊等，不同方向包圍。<br />\n<br />\n2012中環導賞團幾條路分散行，不過當時人唔夠多，佔領唔到咁多路<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2nbNXo2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2nbNXo2.png&h=3828f686&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d5079c4f61d8ce8486345f14d19ac22710d79b16","tid":1383253,"uid":258387,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:20:56.000Z","msg":"佢哋當然都知中共係大佬，但始終我地圍都只係圍到林鄭，因為佢係香港嘅始作俑者嘛。我哋要對準五大訴求嘅話，擒賊先擒王，下下屌啲卒仔好似對於五大訴求冇乜作為。"},{"pid":"a1f4c6fe0a7279f7699a2e8a95950717a14f1cbc","tid":1383253,"uid":258387,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"15c79cff2809615a92c2406a76e606590f8e3dcc","tid":1383253,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:03:20.000Z","msg":"圍你老母 6月講到口臭<br />\n<br />\n見依家個局開始靜 又想叫人衝?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:21:43.000Z","msg":"圍姐，唔係叫你衝。靜坐禮賓府都得。"},{"pid":"7c177d9ae01eed61057e18e7cff585bc51dfde01","tid":1383253,"uid":149844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:24:02.000Z","msg":"陳伯苦行交請願信去禮賓府個陣又少人<br />\n都無人知<br />\n林鄭送中部分已完"},{"pid":"0b92035b26e5ecbd933eb1336b1ca03d049a332d","tid":1383253,"uid":258387,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b2c1f91c471a7ed22c36f7cc50e14688feaf3369","tid":1383253,"uid":33721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:04:40.000Z","msg":"柒婆算得乜 中共先係大佬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:26:06.000Z","msg":"無何否認嘅係我地只可以逼林鄭面對訴求，令佢瞓唔到都好吖。林鄭都未搞掂，何況終極大佬。"},{"pid":"3d4ffd7e752e32c119b9e2b91be9d552211830b8","tid":1383253,"uid":258387,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7c177d9ae01eed61057e18e7cff585bc51dfde01","tid":1383253,"uid":149844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:24:02.000Z","msg":"陳伯苦行交請願信去禮賓府個陣又少人<br />\n都無人知<br />\n林鄭送中部分已完"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:26:37.000Z","msg":"所以我哋係唔係應該認真搞一次？"},{"pid":"fe4358b3684677950738e4775df518813f9acfa9","tid":1383253,"uid":258387,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8f6102d10fb505886f725a900d37c6b40665dd3e","tid":1383253,"uid":89974,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"quote":{"pid":"53f46b5e2a43e57338ff31e250857dacaef48cc2","tid":1383253,"uid":258387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:00:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},